REQUIREMENTS

* This package needs apertium-3.1 and lttoolbox-3.1 packages installed in the
system.

DESCRIPTION

THis program is mainly based on the ER found in Freeling...


When building, this package generates the following modules:

* apertium-pn-recogniser
  Deformatters for html, rtf and txt document formats. Execute without parameters to see the usage.

* apertium-pn-recogniser-final

